  <h2>How are points calculated?</h2>
  <h3>Elimination Points</h3>
  <p>
    Elimination points will play a pretty big role in the amount of points you get, especially when playing in Duo and Squad matched.
  </p>
  <p>Elimination points are based off the match type:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Solo: 10 points
    </li>
    <li>
      Duo: 20 points
    </li>
    <li>
      Squad: 40 points
    </li>
  </ul>
  
